Day 27 of #circuitbreaker: Dalgona Coffee SUCCESS! 🥳 1st try I failed coz I used the wrong coffee powder. 2nd try with @nescafe_sg powder - Yay!!! 💥 ⁣
⁣
Finally checked this off my to-do list during this CB. Foam not enough or maybe my cup is too big, need to double the portion next time 😋⁣
⁣
Recipe: ⁣
- 2 tbsp Coffee Power⁣
- 2 tbsp Sugar ⁣
- 2 tbsp Hot Water ⁣
- Milk & Ice! ⁣
⁣
Served! 🤤⁣
